content: Remember to take breaks once in a while!
You are going to own it today.
TIME IS SO FINITE, SPEND IT WITH THE ONES YOU LOVE
MAKE SURE YOU LOVE YOURSELF, YOU SEXY HUMAN
KEEP GOING! Unless you need to take a break... then do that instead. :)
WHATEVER YOU DO TODAY, OWN THAT SHIT.
You can't say no one loves you if you love yourself ;) (because you technically count as a someone)
To wish you were someone else is to waste the person you are.
It all starts with a single step.
When you say yes to others, make sure you're not saying no to yourself!
Please, please, please make healthy decisions!
